$lang['Similarly, after reaching 9 in Hexadecimal (represented by “F”), we start counting again at 10 (“10”). This pattern continues until we reach 15 (“1F”), at which point we reset back to 0 and begin counting again at 16 (“20”). This might sound confusing at first, but with a little practice, it will become second nature!'] = 'Lykas, nei it berikken fan 9 yn hexadesimale (fertsjintwurdige troch &quot;F&quot;), begjinne wy ​​​​wer te tellen op 10 (&quot;10&quot;). Dit patroan giet troch oant wy 15 (&quot;1F&quot;) berikke, op hokker punt wy weromsette nei 0 en opnij begjinne te tellen op 16 (&quot;20&quot;). Dit kin earst betiizjend klinke, mar mei in bytsje oefening sil it twadde natuer wurde!';
